# Documentation & status updates

- If code behavior, CLI, env vars, or setup steps change:
  - Update `README.md` and/or the relevant `*SUMMARY.md`.
- Always update `IMPLEMENTATION_STATUS.md`:
  - What was done
  - What remains
  - Test status (passed/failed + command)
